<p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">根据《关于做好江西省2023年普通高校专升本考试招生报名工作的通知》（赣考院普[2022]18号）</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">有关要求，为保证</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">我校</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">退役大学生士兵专升本</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">免试录取</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">综合评价</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">工作公平、公正、公开，特制定</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">本招生简章。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">一、</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">组织</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">机构</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.学校成立2023年专升本招生工作领导小组，全面负责学校2023年专升本招生工作，制定2023年专升本招生工作政策，决定有关2023年专升本招生的重大事宜。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.学校招生就业处是组织和实施2023年专升本招生工作的常设机构，具体负责学校2023年专升本招生日常工作。未授权或委托任何中介（培训）机构或个人开展2023年专升本招生活动。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3.学校纪检部门对2023年专升本招生工作实施监督，负责监督招生工作各项政策和规定的落实，维护广大考生和学校的合法权益。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">4.学校</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">成立</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">退役大学生士兵专升本</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">免试录取</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">综合评价</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">工作小组，全面负责我校</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">退役大学生</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">专升本免试考生</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">的综合评价</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">工作。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">二、招生对象</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">在2023年7月31日前可取得或已取得毕业证的退役大学生士兵，且符合下列条件之一：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.江西省普通高校高职（专科）学生在校期间或毕业后应征入伍。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.外省普通高校高职（专科）学生在校期间或毕业后，在江西应征入伍。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">三、报名条件</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">考生报考需同时满足以下基本条件：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.遵守《中华人民共和国宪法》及其他法律法规。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.身体状况符合相关要求。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3.高职（专科）学习期间无记过及以上纪律处分，或受到纪律处分但报名前已解除处分的。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">4.在入伍期间和退役后工作学习期间，无记过及以上纪律处分，或受到纪律处分但报名前已解除处分的。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">四、招生专业及计划数</span></p><table cellspacing="0" width="1000" height="420"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased" class="firstRow"><td valign="center" width="55" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: windowtext; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: bottom; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 1px;margin-left: 1px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;overflow-wrap: break-word"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">序号</span></strong></p></td><td valign="center" width="95" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: windowtext; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: bottom; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 1px;margin-left: 1px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;overflow-wrap: break-word"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">专业代码</span></strong></p></td><td valign="center" width="171" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: windowtext; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: bottom; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 1px;margin-left: 1px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialias