g: antialiased"><td colspan="3" valign="center" width="321" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 7px; border-top: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: bottom; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 1px;margin-left: 1px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;overflow-wrap: break-word"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">合计</span></p></td><td valign="center" width="107" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 7px; border-top: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: bottom; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 1px;margin-left: 1px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;overflow-wrap: break-word"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">178</span></p></td><td valign="center" width="103" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 7px; border-top: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: bottom; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1.42857; text-align: center; background-repeat: repeat-x; overflow-wrap: break-word;" height="30"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">五、考查时间及办法</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">综合评价考查采取线下面试的形式，将全程录像并保存备查，学校纪检监察部门对面试全过</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">程进行监督。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 41px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">（一）</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">面试报名及考查时间</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.报名时间：凡符合免试申请条件的退役大学生士兵于2023年3月1日9:00-3月9日17:00自行登录江西软件职业技术大学官网</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">（</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">网址：</span><a href="http://www.jxuspt.com/%EF%BC%89/%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%93%E5%8D%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%8A%A5%E5%90%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3/%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A1%AB%E5%86%99%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%88%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%8F%B7%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E4%B8%93%E7%A7%91%E6%AF%95%E4%B8%9A%E9%99%A2%E6%A0%A1%E3%80%81%E6%8A%A5%E8%80%83%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E5%9C%A8%E6%A0%A1%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E6%88%90%E7%BB%A9%E3%80%81%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AF%81%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E3%80%81%E9%80%80%E4%BC%8D%E8%AF%81%E6%98%8E%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E7%AD%89%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E3%80%82" style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(51, 122, 183);padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">http://www.jxuspt.com/）“专升本报名入口”，按要求填写、上传个人基本信息（包括本人手机号）、专科毕业院校、报考专业等相关信息。</span></a></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.面试时间：</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">20</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">23</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">年</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">月</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">13日14:00</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 41px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">（二）</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">携带材料</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.报名</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">时间：本人身份证原件、复印件1份；</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.退伍证原件、复印件1份；</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3.大学期间成绩原件、复印件；</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">4.《江西软件职业技术大学2023年退役大学生士兵专升本免试申请表》（附件1）。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">（三）面试地点</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">江西软件职业技术大学退役军人教育学院</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">（四）面试方案</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">选聘专家。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">按专业大类分组，每组</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">由3位专家组成，其中1名主考。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">面试命题。面试命题采用现场出题的方式，面试专家组提前1小时现场命题。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3.</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">考生面试。考生提前</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">30</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">分钟</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">到达</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">候考</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">室核验身份、</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">签到</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">、提交材料，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">按</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">指定</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">顺序逐一</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">进入面试室</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">面试</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">由考生随机</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">抽选面试题目</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">回答</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">4.综合</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">成绩评定。面试专家根据考生</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">现</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">场表现打分。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">（</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">五</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">）</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">综合</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">成绩</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">评定规则：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.综合</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">成绩按百分制</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">从以下方面评定：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">（</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">1）</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">报考专业</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">职业适应性或职业技能</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">的掌握情况占60</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">%</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">（</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">2）</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">综合素质</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">占</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">40%，包括语言表达能力、逻辑思维能力、应变能力、职业兴趣等。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.综合</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">成绩为报考专业</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">职业适应性或职业技能</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">的掌握情况、综合素质</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">二</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">项</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">成绩</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">之和。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">评分根据评委现场打分取其</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">平均</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">值</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">(保留2位小数点)作为考生最终成绩。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3.学校招就处</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">将</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">综合成绩</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">在</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">学校官网</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">公示</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">个工作日</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">并在规定时间内向江西省教育考试院上报综合评价合格名单。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">六、录取办法</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">录取工作贯彻公开、公平、公正原则，严格按照教育厅有关文件执行：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.严格执行梯度志愿顺序投档录取原则；</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.学校按专业门类招生计划数依据综合评价总成绩从高分至低分的顺序择优录取，如遇综合总成绩相同时，按专业技能考察成绩排序择优录取，若专业技能考察成绩相同，则再次组织参加学校面试择优录取。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3.若招生类别专业第一志愿未录取完成，学校根据江西省教育考试院提供的第二志愿报考江西软件职业技术大学考生名单，按第一志愿录取的工作流程进行。以此类推，直至征集志愿录取结束。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">4.凡符合录取条件的考生，不得要求学校退档，学校也不得以考生自愿放弃为由退档。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">七、资格审查</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">我校严格按照教育部和省教育厅有关规定对被录取考生进行资格审查，资格审查贯穿考试录取入学全过程，对不符合报名条件、录取条件的考生，确认后一律取消资格。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">八、学费和待遇</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.进入本科阶段学习的学生，按学校2021级规定的学费收费标准交纳有关费用。“专升本”学生享受普通本科生相同的待遇。学生学习期满，各科成绩合格，由学校颁发专科起点的本科毕业证书和学位证书。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.退学退费办法：如学生有特殊原因要求退学，我校按照江西省教育厅《江西省民办高校退学退费办法》的规定，办理退学退费手续。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">九、学习形式</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21.3333px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89);text-indent: 42.6667px">升入本科阶段学习的学生，由我校报省级教育行政部门审核后，在学籍学历信息管理平台注册学籍。视录取情况单独开班或插入本科三年级相同或相近专业学习，学费按所录取专业的学费和住宿收费标准缴纳，享受统招本科生相同待遇。学习期满，各科成绩合格，由我校按照教育部有关文件要求颁发本科毕业证书，其毕业证书上标注“在本校XX专业专科起点本科学习”，学习时间按进入本科阶段学习的实际时间填写。符合学位授予条件者，授予学位证书。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">十、</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">相关要求</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">（</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">一</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">）</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">工作人员</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.面试</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">期间关闭通讯工具</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">公正、客观，独立判断，不得徇私舞弊</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">3.面试</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">过程中严肃、认真。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">（</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">二</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">）</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">参加</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">面试</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">考生</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">参加</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">面试</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">的考生须携带本人有效身份证件</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">在</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">面试候考</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">室内</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">交给工作人员</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">核验、登记</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">2.</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">面试时按照面试题目口述回答问题并回答评委</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">现场</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">提问。如发现有任何违纪行为，立即取消面试资格和面试成绩。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 黑体;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">十一、招生咨询、信息发布及监督</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.在2023年专升本招生咨询中，本校咨询人员的意见、建议仅作为考生填报志愿的参考，不属学校录取承诺。学校招生录取有关信息通过印制报考指南、江西软件职业技术大学招生信息网、教育部及各省（区、市）招生主管部门的专升本信息平台等渠道统一发布。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">学校地址：江西省南昌市先锋创客小镇</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 43px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 21px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">邮政编码：330041</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51,